=== Noun ===
'''river''' ([[rivers]])

#A large [[stream]] of water that alters the nearby landscape.  Occassionally rivers overflow their [[bank]]s and cause a [[flood]].
#Any large flow of a [[liquid]] in a single body (e.g. 'a river of blood').

